<section class="section" id="vhl-schedules">
    <div class="container">

        <div class="vhl-logo">
            <h1 class="title">Schedules</h1>
            <img class="logo" src="/images/vhl-logo.png" alt="Virtual Hitting Leagues"/>
        </div>
        <hr>

        <div class="content">
            <p>Each league will run for five weeks. Weeks 1-4 will makeup the Regular Season in which teams will each play two 6-inning games against different opponents. Week 5 will be for the indidual Home Run Derby, Hitting Contest, and Team Playoffs. Please see the <a href="/vhl-about">About VHL</a> page for more information. To register for an upcoming League, either click through below or check out our <a href="/events">Upcoming Events</a> page.</p>
        </div>

        {{#if vhlEvents}}
            {{# vhlEvents }}
                <article class="media event">
                    <div class="media-left">
                        <div class="date">
                            <span class="month">{{{formatDate date=fields.startDate format='MMM'}}}</span>
                            <span class="day">{{{formatDate date=fields.startDate format='D'}}}</span>
                            <span class="dayofweek">{{{formatDate date=fields.startDate format='ddd'}}}</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="media-content">
                        <div class="info">
                            {{#ifCond fields.eventCost '>' 0}}
                                <span class="tag is-success">${{ fields.eventCost }}</span>
                            {{else}}
                                <span class="tag is-success">Free</span>
                            {{/ifCond}}
                            <a class="title name is-4" href="/event/{{ sys.id }}">{{ fields.eventName }}</a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="content">{{ fields.introText }}</div>
                    </div>
                </article>
            {{/ vhlEvents }}
        {{else}}
            <div class="no-events">There are no upcoming Virtual Hitting Leagues at this time.</div>
        {{/if}}

    </div>
</section>
